page: Naa Peru Surya, Naa Illu India
message: The film was released on 4 May 2018. The film was a box office success and was declared "Hit". After the its success it was dubbed in Tamil as En Peyar Surya, En Veedu India and in Malayalam as Ente Peru Surya Ente Veedu India and later in Hindi as Surya: The Soldier on 7 September 2018.
